1/26/28/29M/203C/208/211/211A/213X/214/215X/219X/W2<br />\n<br />\n荃灣及葵青區巴士服務<br />\n<br />\n暫停服務：30/30X/31/31M/32H/32M/33A/34/34M/35A/35X/36/36A/36B/36M/37/38/38A/39A/40/41M/42A/42C/42M/43/43A/43B/43M/51/234A/234B/234X/235M/238M/243M<br />\n<br />\n屯門及元朗區巴士服務<br />\n<br />\n暫停服務：53/57M/58M/59M/60M/60X/61M/61X/62X/63X/66M/67M/67X/68A/68M/69M/258D/259D/261X/263/265M/268C/268M/269C/269D/269M<br />\n<br />\n沙田，大埔及北區巴士服務<br />\n<br />\n暫停服務：40X/43X/46X/47A/47X/48X/49X/72/72A/72X/73X/74A/75X/80/80K/80M/80X/81/81K/82B/82K/82X/83K/83X/84M/85/85A/85B/85K/86/86A/86K/87B/88/88K/88X/89/89B/89X/249X/270A/270B/271/278X/280X/281A/282/283/284/286X/287X/288/289R/299X/848/868/887/888/889/891/W3<br />\n<br />\n西貢區巴士服務<br />\n<br />\n暫停服務：91M/95/98D/290/290A/290X/296D<br />\n<br />\n有咩問題可以inbox我哋<br />\n<br />\n#九巴 #kmb"},{"pid":"7d2ffee23903ff1866b701b74a98fefdd4307917","tid":1608262,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1f139b25ce914fa808549446304686ef7aaedaf0","tid":1608262,"uid":118665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:14:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b51391f61968aaad13528b78ce63a2d7e11844a3","tid":1608262,"uid":184261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"(17:14) 位處灣仔一帶市民，如有需要，可在安全情況下到灣仔碼頭離開：<br />\n<br />\n上車點：會議道「灣仔碼頭」對開<br />\n<br />\n2A 往耀東（經北角、鰂魚涌、太古）<br />\n2X 往筲箕灣（經西灣河）<br />\n8 往杏花村（經柴灣斜）<br />\n8P 往小西灣（經漁灣邨）<br />\n40 往華富（經半山區、薄扶林道、置富）<br />\n104 往紅隧口（特別服務）<br />\n960 往建生（經良景、大興、屯門市中心）"},{"pid":"26038c5819b7cf3a3bf8d7c0868fdbc9bf3359df","tid":1608262,"uid":315604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:21:05.000Z","msg":"金鐘嗰邊可以點走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb54c04d5de97222b35f59d57390147fd38fa5b8","tid":1608262,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26038c5819b7cf3a3bf8d7c0868fdbc9bf3359df","tid":1608262,"uid":