br />\n(17:41) 根據前線職員消息，上環港澳碼頭巴士總站已沒有巴士服務。 <br />\n<br />\n據現場觀察，附近皇后街巴士站經西區海底隧道過海的服務並不穩定。<br />\n<br />\n如需離開該範圍，可考慮使用港鐵上環站， 中環渡輪碼頭， 或往堅尼地城的電車服務。"},{"pid":"ec87f8a39d6302d52ed96ed9bed7d5b876bd1afb","tid":1608262,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n封撚晒 根本無路走<br />\n<br />\n街坊接仔返歸打麻將先係正解 屯門輕鐵路仲有好多人<br />\n<br />\n出面都係"},{"pid":"54232cb2a4fcd055ce6dda76224953fd6babc916","tid":1608262,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"手足見車/船就上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好理去邊"},{"pid":"69ecc0baee6ce871a601aa4ee58248b5f3de951a","tid":1608262,"uid":174936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3275f6717fd44b91768fcc33d0111e4f1531e9d5","tid":1608262,"uid":209599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:53:02.000Z","msg":"大圍仲有咩交通工具?"},{"pid":"1f0a2720f8e8b3624a131ce0c1c656eb6a66ccc5","tid":1608262,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3275f6717fd44b91768fcc33d0111e4f1531e9d5","tid":1608262,"uid":209599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:53:02.000Z","msg":"大圍仲有咩交通工具?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"全個沙田區冇晒巴士<br />\n大圍站好似仲有黨鐵"},{"pid":"16f7931e236e75eeb566f2590a761c85d6d86145","tid":1608262,"uid":173640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:59:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e141e0e9f0b9217391540ff91d883b258085bbec","tid":1608262,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:59:44.000Z","msg":"1751 石門站 已關閉"},{"pid":"66214385cf6f8f9e56ae89f31559ddf92a85db4f","tid":1608262,"uid":154486,"like":0,"d